 will never fly</li>\r\n	<li>Favorite trick: Cutback</li>\r\n	<li>Favorite spot: Echo Beach</li>\r\n	<li>Hobbies: Skateboard and Biking</li>\r\n  </ul>\r\n  </div>\r\n  <div class=\"frame\">\r\n  <p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><a href=\"http://lets-surf.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/suta-1.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-74 photo\" src=\"http://lets-surf.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/suta-1-300x200.jpg\" alt=\"suta 1\" width=\"300\" height=\"200\" /></a></p>\r\n  </div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"article even\">\r\n <h2>Sodok</h2>\r\n  <div class=\"frame\">\r\n <p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><a href=\"http://wordpress.planeur-abbeville.fr/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/sodok2.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-304 photo\" src=\"http://wordpress.planeur-abbeville.fr/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/sodok2-300x300.jpg\" alt=\"sodok2\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" /></a></p>\r\n  </div>\r\n\r\n  <div class=\"elt-text\">\r\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;\">\r\n	<li>Motto: Victory is always possible for the person who refuses to stop fighting</li>\r\n	<li>Favorite trick: Snap 360 blow tail</li>\r\n	<li>Favorite spot: Echo beach</li>\r\n	<li>Hobbies: hiking and football</li>\r\n  </ul>\r\n  </div>\r\n  <div class=\"frame\">\r\n  <p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><a href=\"http://wordpress.planeur-abbeville.fr/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/sodok1.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-303 photo\" src=\"http://wordpress.planeur-abbeville.fr/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/sodok1-300x188.jpg\" alt=\"sodok1\" width=\"300\" height=\"188\" /></a></p>\r\n  </div>\r\n</div>'),(424,649,'_menu_item_type','post_type'),(425,649,'_menu_item_menu_item_parent','0'),(426,649,'_menu_item_object_id','56'),(427,649,'_menu_item_object','page'),(428,649,'_menu_item_target',''),(429,649,'_menu_item_classes','a:1:{i:0;s:0:\"\";}'),(430,649,'_menu_item_xfn',''),(431,649,'_menu_item_url',''),(433,650,'_edit_lock','1432034681:1'),(434,650,'_edit_last','2'),(