ng to the conditions.</li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align: justify; font-size: 15px;\">Surf Board Rent</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n[/et_pb_cta][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section][et_pb_section fullwidth=\"off\" specialty=\"off\" transparent_background=\"off\" background_color=\"#404040\" inner_shadow=\"off\" parallax=\"off\" parallax_method=\"off\" module_id=\"massage\"][et_pb_row][et_pb_column type=\"2_3\"][et_pb_cta admin_label=\"Massage - Content\" button_url=\"#\" button_text=\"Book Your Course Now\" use_background_color=\"off\" background_color=\"#\" background_layout=\"dark\" text_orientation=\"center\" module_class=\"ncf_trigger_element\"]\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify; font-weight: 900;\">Massage</h2>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 15px; text-align: justify;\">After hours of surfing when all of your muscles are sore, a massage is a perfect way to end the day. Our experienced masseuse can provide ayurvédic massage, a deep tissue massage that is perfect for surfers.</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 15px; text-align: justify;\">price : 200.000 IDR</p>\r\n\r\n[/et_pb_cta][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=\"1_3\"][et_pb_blurb admin_label=\"Massage\" url_new_window=\"off\" use_icon=\"off\" icon_color=\"#68beac\" use_circle=\"off\" circle_color=\"#68beac\" use_circle_border=\"off\" circle_border_color=\"#68beac\" image=\"http://lets-surf.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/Massage-280x280.png\" icon_placement=\"top\" animation=\"left\" background_layout=\"light\" text_orientation=\"center\"]\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n[/et_pb_blurb][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section][et_pb_section fullwidth=\"off\" specialty=\"off\" transparent_background=\"off\" background_color=\"#ffffff\" inner_shadow=\"off\" parallax=\"off\" parallax_method=\"off\"][et_pb_row][et_pb_column type=\"1_3\"][et_pb_blurb admin_label=\"Outdoor Yoga\" url_new_window=\"off\" use_icon=\"off\" icon_color=\"#68beac\" use_circle=\"off\" circle_color=\"#68beac\" use_circle_border=\"off\" circle_border_color=\"#68beac\" image=\"http://lets-surf.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/Yoga-280x280.png\" icon_placement=\"top\" animation=\"top\" background_layout=\"light\" text_orientation=\"center\"]\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n[/et_pb_blurb][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=\"2_3\"][et_pb_cta admin_label=\"Outdoor Yoga - Content\" button_url=\"#\" button_text=\"Book Your Course Now\" use_background_color=\"off\" background_color=\"#\" background_layout=\"light\" text_orientation=\"center\" module_class=\"ncf_trigger_element\"]\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify; font-weight: 900;\">Outdoor Yoga</h2>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 15px; text-align: justify;\">The ancient Hindu art of Yoga is the practise of breathing, meditation and body poses which help to promote many health and wellbeing benefits from relaxation to core strength and balance. We conduct Yoga classes daily on some of the finest beaches Bali has to offer. Our instructor, Anouk, is a dedicated Vinyassa and Ying Yoga teacher who studied yoga in Byron Bay and was trained here in Bali. Her classes are designed to help her students improve their balance and gain strength to become better surfers.</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 15px; text-align: justify;\">price : 100.000 IDR</p>\r\n\r\n[/et_pb_cta][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section][et_pb_section fullwidth=\"off\" specialty=\"off\" transparent_background=\"off\" background_color=\"#404040\" inner_shadow=\"off\" parallax=\"off\" parallax_method=\"off\"][et_pb_row][et_pb_column type=\"2_3\"][et_pb_cta admin_label=\"Tour Guide - Content\" button_url=\"#\" button_text=\"Book Your Course Now\" use_background_color=\"off\" background_color=\"#\" background_layout=\"dark\" text_orientation=\"center\" module_class=\"ncf_trigger_element\"]\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify; font-weight: 900;\">Tour Guide</h2>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 15px; text-align: justify;\">Tanah Lot , Ubud , Uluwatu Temple, Amed and much more are amazing landscape you must see if you come in this paradisiaque island. Our driver will bring you to the best place that will make you never want to leave Bali.</p>\r\n\r\n[/et_pb_cta][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=\"1_3\"][et_pb_blurb admin_label=\"Tour\" url_new_window=\"off\" use_icon=\"off\" icon_color=\"#68beac\" use_circle=\"off\" circle_color=\"#68beac\" use_circle_border=\"off\" circle_border_color=\"#68beac\" image=\"http://lets-surf.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/Tour-Guide-280x280.png\" icon_placement=\"top\" animation=\"left\" background_layout=\"light\" text_orientation=\"center\"]\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n[/et_pb_blurb][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section][et_pb_section fullwidth=\"off\" specialty=\"off\"][et_pb_row][et_pb_column type=\"1_3\"][et_pb_blurb admin_label=\"P.Session\" url_new_window=\"off\" use_icon=\"off\" icon_color=\"#68beac\" use_circle=\"off\" circle_color=\"#68beac\" use_circle_border=\"off\" circle_border_color=\"#68beac\" image=\"http://lets-surf.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/Photo-Session-280x280.png\" icon_placement=\"top\" animation=\"right\" background_layout=\"light\" text_orientation=\"center\"]\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n[/et_pb_blurb][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=\"2_3\"][et_pb_cta admin_label=\"Photo Session - Content\" button_url=\"#\" button_text=\"Book Your Course Now\" use_background_color=\"off\" background_color=\"#\" background_layout=\"light\" text_orientation=\"center\" module_class=\"ncf_trigger_element\"]\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify; font-weight: 900;\">Photo Session</h2>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 15px; text-align: justify;\">Don’t miss the opportunity to immortalize your first wave or to capture your best wipe out. Our photographer can take your action shots by request and you will receive a CD of your photos within a few day.</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 15px; text-align: justify;\">price : 400.000 IDR</p>\r\n\r\n[/et_pb_cta][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section][et_pb_section fullwidth=\"off\" specialty=\"off\" transparent_background=\"off\" background_color=\"#404040\" inner_